narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: yes- professor Diaz is a wonderful professor to learn SPanish with
Learn a ton and cover tons of topics. Teacher not very helpful. Class taught entirely in spanish.

Prof. Diaz is a total mensch and a wonderful professor. He cares so much about his students that he only speaks to them in Spanish. Try to listen to him speak as much as possible; I learned more from that than from the text book. I love that he only explains Spanish grammar IN Spanish. 50 minutes of immersion per day will go a long way over the course of a semester! The work is easy and plentiful, the tests are generous, and class is always animated.
I would, but only if they had taken an introductory spanish course before.
